column2: Cells containing a dash (-) indicate that data are unavailable. Estimates are unavailable either because the SA2 labour force estimate did not meet the minimum size or because there is a break in the series caused by the shift from the 2011 to the 2016 ASGS. For more information, see SALM Methodology page on the National Skills Commission (NSC) website and the 2016 ASGS changeover user guide (also available from the NSC website).
